Argentina ' s Banco Rio to be listed in September . Argentina ' s Banco Rio de la Plata is to be stock listed in the United States and in Europe at the end of September , state news agency Telam reported Monday . Spanish bank Santander bought a controlling stake in Banco Rio for $ 594 million in May , at which time it stated its intention to list the Argentine bank . Santander will manage the stock issue in Europe and Merrill Lynch will be in charge in the United States , Telam said , quoting Banco Rio officials . The equity issue will take place through a " book building " system . ( ( - - Axel Bugge , Buenos Aires Newsroom , 541 318 - 0668 ) ) . 
